EN: This short-haired cat is easy to take care of.

ZH: 他坐在一个矮桌前画画。
EN: He sat at a short table painting.

ZH: 那幅画太短，需要再加些颜色。
EN: The painting is too short, it needs more colors.

ZH: 周末的假期总是短暂的。
EN: Weekend holidays are always short.
